Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.25,0:18:04.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}从通风道出去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.16,0:18:15.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}怎么样子还是那么难看呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.01,0:18:23.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}停下！快闪开
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.56,0:18:24.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.48,0:18:24.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.07,0:18:28.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}呀——
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.84,0:19:09.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}目标企图使用强力溶解液，直接侵入总部
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.78,0:19:10.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.60,0:19:12.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}还用说？当然是干掉他了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.89,0:19:16.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}所以我才问怎么办，步枪已经掉下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.08,0:19:17.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}背后的电池也被切断了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.41,0:19:19.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}还有三分钟就不能动了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.17,0:19:22.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}我有作战方案了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.91,0:19:24.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}留在这里的机器进行防御
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.06,0:19:28.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}中和 A.T.field 保护攻击手不受溶解液伤害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.02,0:19:32.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}后卫下去把步枪捡回来，交给攻击手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.54,0:19:36.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}然后攻击手用步枪扫射消灭目标
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.25,0:19:38.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}这样行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.55,0:19:40.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}可以，我来当前卫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.34,0:19:43.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}不巧，我要当前卫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.24,0:19:44.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}这很危险呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.99,0:19:46.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}正是因为如此呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.58,0:19:51.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}不还你上次的人情我会觉得不舒服的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.43,0:19:54.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}真嗣当攻击手，优等生当后卫，——如何
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.86,0:19:56.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}——明白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.50,0:20:02.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(50,50)}那么，动手吧
